<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What is dynamic council generation?</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Every time the LocalGov Drupal scenario is deployed, AI creates a completely unique fictional council. This includes:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>A unique council identity</strong> - name, region, theme, and population size</li>
  <li><strong>Tailored content</strong> - 140+ pages of realistic council content</li>
  <li><strong>Custom images</strong> - hero images, councillor headshots, and location photos</li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">
  No two deployments are the same. Your council might be a coastal tourism destination in Cornwall, an industrial heritage town in Yorkshire, or a market town in the Midlands.
</p>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <strong>Why fictional councils?</strong> Using AI-generated fictional councils avoids confusion with real local authorities while demonstrating realistic content patterns and AI capabilities.
  </p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Council identity</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The AI generates a unique council identity with five key components:
</p>

<div class="ndx-identity-grid">
  <div class="ndx-identity-card">
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Council Name</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body-s">
      A realistic but fictional name combining a placename with council type.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s ndx-identity-example">
      <strong>Example:</strong> Thornbridge District Council
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-identity-card">
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Region</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body-s">
      One of 12 UK regions, influencing local references throughout content.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s ndx-identity-example">
      <strong>Regions:</strong> North East, North West, Yorkshire, East Midlands, West Midlands, East of England, London, South East, South West, Wales, Scotland, Northern Ireland
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-identity-card">
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Theme/Character</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body-s">
      A defining characteristic that shapes content and imagery.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s ndx-identity-example">
      <strong>Examples:</strong> Coastal tourism, industrial heritage, market town, university town, historic city, rural district
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-identity-card">
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Population</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body-s">
      A population range that influences service scale references.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s ndx-identity-example">
      <strong>Ranges:</strong> Small (under 50k), Medium (50-150k), Large (over 150k)
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-identity-card">
    <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Flavour Keywords</h4>
    <p class="govuk-body-s">
      Local terms woven into content for authenticity.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s ndx-identity-example">
      <strong>Example:</strong> For coastal: harbour, fishing, tourism, beach, maritime
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

